This Privacy Policy is intended to inform users about the collection and use of personal information by the Spark Swipe. Please read it carefully.

1. Information We Do Not Collect

The Spark Swipe  does not collect any personal information from its users. We do not access, store, or transmit any data about you.

2. Camera and Torch Access

The Spark Swipe  requires access to your device's camera and flashlight to function. This access is solely used to turn on and off the torch. The app does not use the camera for any other purpose and does not capture or record any images or videos.

3. Permissions

The app may request permission to access your device's camera and flashlight. This access is required to provide the core functionality of the app. Please note that we do not misuse these permissions or collect any data without your consent.

4. Third-Party Services

The Spark Swipe  does not integrate with or utilize any third-party services that may collect or share user data.

5. Updates to Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy in the future to comply with changes in regulations or to improve transparency. Any updates will be reflected in the app's description on the app store where you downloaded it.

6. Contact Information

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or the Spark Swipe, please contact us at email.

Last updated: 26 Oct, 2023

Thank you for using the Spark Swipe. Your privacy and trust are important to us.
